<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She was one of five stars sent home during Wednesday night's eviction bloodbath on The Bachelor. </p>

<p>And now blonde bombshell Charley Bond has weighed in on the kiss Bella Varelis and Locky Gilbert shared at the cocktail party that made Roxi Kenny see red.</p>

<p>'I'm all for it. You have to remember where you are. We are on The Bachelor,' the 25-year-old blonde told The Courier Mail on Wednesday.</p>

<p>'I'm all for it!' On Wednesday, Charley Bond (pictured) defended Bella Varelis and Locky Gilbert's cocktail party kiss on The Bachelor </p>

<p>'If my lips were there ready for a smooch from Bach, I'm not going to pull away. I think it's fine,' she told the publication. </p>

<p>On Wednesday night, Roxi was reduced to tears after Locky Gilbert kissed Bella Varelis at the evening's cocktail party - hours after she shared a smooch with the handsome hunk herself. </p>

<p>Viewers of the Channel Ten hit show were left baffled by Roxi's theatrical turn - with some unsure what all the fuss was about.  </p>

<p>Drama: On Wednesday night, Roxi was reduced to tears after Locky Gilbert kissed Bella Varelis at the evening's cocktail party - hours after she shared a smooch with the handsome hunk herself</p>

<p>'You have a rose Roxi, calm down,' Tweeted one viewer.</p>

<p>Meanwhile, a second viewer didn't understand what all the fuss was about. 'Didn't Roxi just kiss Locky like an hour ago? Why is she upset?' they wrote. </p>

<p>A third viewer appeared to be frustrated by Roxi's emotional outbursts, writing: 'Uh, it's called The Bachelor, not the Roxi Drama show.'</p>

<p>And a fourth seemed to share the same sentiment. 'Roxi is that girl who signs up for MasterChef but can't even boil water.'</p>

<p>'You have a rose, calm down!: Fans were left baffled by Roxi's (pictured) emotional outburst after the kiss </p>

<p>In a piece to camera, Locky explained himself.</p>

<p>'There's a process, I'm not trying to hurt anyone, but I am trying to find the person I want to spend the rest of my life with,' he began. </p>

<p>'Roxi, yes, I should have been more respectful of you, but... There's 15 girls here, and I've got connections with other girls besides you. And I'm sorry for that.'</p>

<p>The Bachelor continues Thursday at 7.30pm on Channel Ten </p>

